\s YESU N’UMWAMI W’URUKUNDO RWINSHI
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Yesu n’Umwami w’\bd*\bd U\bd*\bd rukundo rwinshi, kuko \bd*\bd Yikoreye \bd*\bd imibabaro yacu; \bd*\bd Yajanjaguriwe \bd*\bd ivyacu bigabitanyo, igihano cacu cabaye kuri we.\bd*
\pc \bdit N’ukuri, n’izacu ntimba \bdit*\bdit Yishizeko\bdit*\bdit , n\bdit*\bdit ’iyacu mibabaro \bdit*\bdit Yikoreye\bdit*\bdit , tweho \bdit*\bdit twamwiyumviriye nk’uwakubiswe, nk’uwacumiswe n’Imana, akicurikirizwa n’akabonge, kubw’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit ivyaha vyacu; ajanjaguriw’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit ivyacu bigabitanyo, n’urukundo rw’imbura rugero\bdit*\bdit  ./.\bdit*\bdit Kand’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit imishishagu yiwe ni yo idukiza./.\bdit*
